name: Signs and labels on cartons, crates, etc.
text: §147-77  Signs and labels on cartons, crates, etc.  The signs and labels required by section 147-75 shall likewise be affixed to the cartons, crates, and cases containing eggs required to be marked as in the section provided. [L 1953, c 90, §1; RL 1955, §22-75; HRS §147-77]
